{"tid":1067960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[創意] 養生發奇想 女子打果汁針險死","createTime":"2019-03-19T02:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T02:03:33.000Z","uid":56881,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8829dd0af9c18f719f32bacb701980c203edfead","tid":1067960,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:01:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A4%8A%E7%94%9F%E7%99%BC%E5%A5%87%E6%83%B3-%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%89%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%B1%81%E9%87%9D%E9%9A%AA%E6%AD%BB-224432808.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A4%258A%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25A5%2587%25E6%2583%25B3-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%259E%259C%25E6%25B1%2581%25E9%2587%259D%25E9%259A%25AA%25E6%25AD%25BB-224432808.html&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKn4HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=31c77841\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A4%8A%E7%94%9F%E7%99%BC%E5%A5%87%E6%83%B3-%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%89%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%B1%81%E9%87%9D%E9%9A%AA%E6%AD%BB-224432808.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/F2aEZwABjronvJOIQ5H46Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDAw/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/7b24570d75cb57b04891010f4e9ac6d6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FF2aEZwABjronvJOIQ5H46Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F7b24570d75cb57b04891010f4e9ac6d6&h=2a1bcc05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾女士（右）將混合果汁靜脈注射入體內。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n【本報綜合報道】湖南郴州桂陽縣一名女子注重養生，卻盲目行事，<span style=\"color: red;\">竟在家中以鮮榨果汁替自己進行靜脈注射</span>，導致多個器官受損，結果要送院緊急救治，幸好及時獲得治療，否則危及性命。<br />\n<br />\n五十一歲的曾女士平日健康良好，但步入更年期後開始沉迷鑽研養生之道，連偏方也願意嘗試。上月廿二日，她忽發奇想，在家中將廿多種水果混合榨汁，過濾後替自己進行靜脈注射。事後她感到皮膚痕癢、體溫上升，卻不以為意。當晚丈夫察覺有異，她才道出原委，被送院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n多個器官受損<br />\n該院重症醫學科醫生指曾女士全身感染嚴重，凝血功能出現障礙，肝臟、腎臟、心臟等主要器官受不同程度損傷。若不及時救治，恐出現大出血、多器官衰竭以至休克。醫院一方面透過臨床血液淨化，清除曾女士血液內的異物，另一方面替她進行抗感染、護肝、護心等藥物治療，同時大量輸入凝血因子。<br />\n<br />\n經過五天救治，曾女士器官功能逐漸恢復，現已脫離危險。她說原以為新鮮水果含有豐富營養，對身體有好處，誰知養生險養出禍來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68814f715921de87477027049c9a461f29d7e17f","tid":1067960,"uid":226622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:03:07.000Z","msg":"咁快發功爭達爾文獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191b29fcbb5d8e79b5347c69d9a26747dd2b7ed9","tid":1067960,"uid":45830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T02:03:33.000Z","msg":"ON9係有樣睇架"}]}